title: The moving candlelight vigil held in Oregon last night
text:
The moving candlelight vigil held in Oregon last night 
Published By: Mashable - Today 
Hours after tragedy struck a community college in Roseburg, Oregon, thousands across the state gathered at vigils commemorating victims.
